Colonna Wins Third Stage at Valencia Cycling Tour
MADRID , February 26 ( Xinhua ) -- Italian sprinter Federico Colonna outmanoeuvred his rivals to snatch victory in the third stage of the Tour of Valencia on Thursday .
Frenchman Pascal Chanteur kept the overall leader 's jersey .
Italian Mario Traversoni finished second and Francois Simon of France was third .
The Tour continues on Friday with the potentially-decisive fourth stage which includes two first category climbs and a second category hill 15 kilometers from the finishing line in Segorbe .
